    "m_Title": "3. Metallic",
    "m_Content": "We will use another Branch to set the Metallic property of the Fragment shader. This will be identical to the Branch we used to set the Alpha, but when the predicate evaluates to False, we want the Metallic property to be 0 rather than 0.8.",
